          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have done my entire schooling from Sherwood Convent School, Gurgaon (Nursery to XII) and have the fondest memories throughout.\nThe school atmosphere is warm and had some amazing teachers who encourage the students in all possible ways.\nThe academic track and extra curriculum balance out each other very well. Teachers are passionate about seeing their students succeed.\nI personally participated in all possible activities and was the vice head girl in XI and XII. The Principal personally committed to doing new things that enhance the academic experience.The school staff is friendly and the overall administration is smooth.\nI will always carry my school in my heart - it made my learning fun and creative.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Sherwood Convent School - DLF Phase 2"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Anita Sharma"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-01-08",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As parents we always want the best for our child and I could not have asked for more since my daughter joined Sherwood Convent School. I am grateful to the faculty for giving personal attention to every student which made them feel important and comforted! This not only made them confident about themselves but moulded their lives for the future too. Respected Principal ma'am and  her team were always welcoming to the parents too with any suggestion. Best experience ever for my child and for us!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Sherwood Convent School - DLF Phase 2"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Muskan Vaid"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-01-08",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As children we would be told that School is our second home as we spent half of our day there, but that acceptance never came from my heart because how could one consider school their home? A place that gave us home-works, assignments, tests and snatched away the fun out of our childhood! It was finally in my beloved school, Sherwood Convent, where I realized and understood that school was in fact a home away from home! This school has given me everything I am today, the skills, the confidence and humility. Despite shifting to this school late i.e., in the IX standard, I felt at ease within a week, and even though this prestigious school was the sixth school of my life, it'll always be \"the'' school for me! I cannot be grateful enough to the esteemed faculty who brought out the best in me. Kudos to our respected Principal ma'am and the entire team for doing a splendid job in nurturing the lives of many! I highly recommend this school to everyone. :) ",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Sherwood Convent School - DLF Phase 2"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Shivangi Kashyap"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-01-04",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I passed out from this school 2 years back and have only great things to say about my experience. The teachers are amazing. Along with the curriculum teachers share their experiences which makes the learning for each student easy. Everyone is treated with care. I have been in this school for 14 long years starting from nursery to 12th and the bond I created with all of them present here is incredible!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
